name: eosjs-keygen

scripts.build: npm run docs && npm run build_browser
scripts.build_browser: npm run build_lib && mkdir -p dist && browserify -o dist/eosjs-keygen.js -s kos lib/index.js
scripts.build_browser_test: npm run build_lib && mkdir -p dist && browserify -o dist/mocha-test.js lib/*.test.js
scripts.prepublishOnly: npm run build_lib && npm run prepublishOnly_test && npm run docs
